instructions: put the charger in the bottom middle of the place mat
put the dinner fork directly to the left of the charger
put the dinner knife directly to the right of the charger
put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork
put the salad knife to the right of the dinner knife
put the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife
put the dessert spoon horizontally above the charger facing left
put the dessert fork below the dessert spoon facing right
put the bread plate to the left of the dessert spoon and a dinner plate on top of the charger
put the butter knife diagonally on the break plate facing up
put the water glass to the left of the dessert fork
put a folded napkin on top of the plate
